plot: While Los Lobos' score plays, the narrator with the voice of cowboy and humorist Will Rogers, tells a true story about sharpshooter Annie Oakley, the last heroin of the Wild West and a lasting star of Buffalo Bill's famous Wild West Show.
title: Rabbit Ears: Annie Oakley
